snippet.title: VideoGame "Garry"s Worst Fear" the 8 legged nightmare
snippet.description:
Garry's worst fear is a TopDown point and click, turn based fighting game.
through garry's eyes you must face his worst fears in his nightmare
Play here : https://bulletaxel.itch.io/garrys-worst-fear

the music and the sound effects were made by Alkahest.
cover made by Constantin SAVALLI-CROCHERAY

Axel Bullet: https://www.instagram.com/axeldumanoir/?hl=fr
ALKAHEST : https://www.instagram.com/alka_mnr/
Constantin : https://www.instagram.com/imaginecsc/


Thanks to Maxence for the graphic assets.
